room_title: Escape room "Abducted" by Seattle Escape Games in Seattle
room_description:
Youâ€™ve just opened your eyes to darkness, feeling weak and confused. The last thing you remember is sitting down to a camp fire with your friends... You've been Abducted!

Footsteps, someone is pacing on the other side of the wall and speaking in a demanding tone, so you lean in and listen... A man is rehearsing and repeating the same lines, over and over. "This is a test of wills and wit. All of your friends have been brought here along with you. Solve all my puzzles in 60 minutes or less in order to save yourself and your friends." The pacing stops, its silent and a clock begins a countdown. The man knows you were listening.

Now the only option is to begin, and beat him at his own game. Can you solve everything? Will you find your friends and make it out in time?
